OL,6,FAn investigation into allegations of   
OL,7,Fbullying and discrimination at         
OL,8,FBritain's equality watchdog has been   
OL,9,Fpaused.                                
OL,11,FThe claims by staff are made against   
OL,12,FBaroness Falkner, the head of the      
OL,13,FEquality and Human Rights Commission   
OL,14,F(EHRC), and other members of its board.
OL,16,FDetails of the allegations were        
OL,17,Freported by Channel 4 News on Tuesday. 
OL,19,FA spokesman for the EHRC said it is now
OL,20,Fseeking legal advice "on the impact of 
OL,21,Fleaked confidential information".      
